Heavenly the beautiful kingdom, &lt;br/&gt;
Blessed is he who cometh there. &lt;br/&gt;
Life eternal, &lt;br/&gt;
Fire bright&lt;br/&gt;
Of the Holy Spirit. &lt;br/&gt;
